wikipedia_page.main: Sunil Seth (born 22 August 1990 in London), also known as Sunny Seth, is an English-born Guyanese squash player who represents Guyana. He achieved a career-high world ranking of 122 in January 2015. He has represented Guyana at the 2014 Commonwealth Games, the 2015 Pan American Games and the 2018 Commonwealth Games.
